{"tid":1614374,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"行動post-大家聽日一齊出旺角保護學生","createTime":"2019-10-02T18:28:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T18:33:00.000Z","uid":151174,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5c766fab70d9b1942fc975d319a7a9e8f1b4dadc","tid":1614374,"uid":151174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:28:44.000Z","msg":"聖公會諸聖中學公然打壓黃絲學生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1612855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1612855</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n承接上一個post，學生自發搞左一個活動，依家怕附近嘅藍絲或者學校報警，大家都知道警狗最鍾意蝦學生，大家聽日3:30一齊出嚟保護佢哋！<br />\n<br />\n其實今日已經有藍絲話要報警，我真係怕啲學生會有危險，求下你地聽日一齊出嚟幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ibk04RB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fibk04RB.png&h=43a9ae82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學生整合事件：<br />\n罷課學生係地下唱榮光歸香港，之後無端端有人問侯罷課學生媽媽，同埋鬧佢地垃圾，態度輕佻，高舉國旗同唱國歌。之後罷課學生等到小息就去佢地班房拍門問佢咩事，幾秒後校長就衝入黎帶走罷課學生，唱國歌學生冇帶走。然後9個罷課學生一齊見副校及社工直至放學，及後見完之後詢問唱國歌學生有冇被召見時，副校回應「有社工去傾」「我地兩個人冇可能同時去哂兩邊㗎喎」"},{"pid":"89a5cba26e3d7b4511ac3f7e312c6f820ebd3a8e","tid":1614374,"uid":151174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:29:07.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"39a1e1b4a1cf7d062ebd465c49c922ab940af626","tid":1614374,"uid":151174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:30:21.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"1d7428fa770dd5537b049282ecbb02418ccfc07a","tid":1614374,"uid":151174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:31:41.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"5ee4924f2a72e5ada02ed15e3aae8fc7cf122c65","tid":1614374,"uid":151174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:31:53.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"36926598edb69729592f59595ca3a3a9cc0e26d1","tid":1614374,"uid":151174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:32:04.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"10b03f678171bc67fab8711a942de9